<p></p>
<p>Sure! Here=E2=80=99s a <strong>clear table of access modifiers</strong> =
in OOP (Java-style), showing <strong>visibility and usage</strong>:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"37=
c62c9c-4ce3-4c66-b2bb-ae5f2baff7f3" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Access Modifier</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Keyword</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Visibility / Scope</strong></p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p><strong>Example Use</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Private</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>private</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Accessible <strong>only within the same class</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Hiding data members (<code>balance</code> in BankAccount)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Default / Package-Private</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><em>(no keyword)</em></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Accessible <strong>within the same package</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Classes in the same package can use it</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Protected</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>protected</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Accessible <strong>within the same package + subclasses</strong></p></td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Parent class wants children to access members</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Public</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>public</code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Accessible <strong>from anywhere</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>API methods meant to be used by all classes</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"ObjectOrientedProgramming(OOP)-=F0=9F=94=B9QuickNotes:">=F0=9F=94=
=B9 Quick Notes:</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Private</strong> =E2=86=92 highest level of encapsulation (data =
hiding).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Default</strong> =E2=86=92 used when no modifier is written; pac=
kage-level access.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Protected</strong> =E2=86=92 useful for inheritance, allows chil=
d classes to access members.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Public</strong> =E2=86=92 no restrictions, everyone can access.<=
/p></li>
</ul>
