<p>Multiple Inheritance</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Number of Parent Classes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>One</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>More than one</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Complexity</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Simple</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Can be complex (diamond problem)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
