<p>=E2=9C=85 <strong>Summary:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Single inheritance</strong> =E2=86=92 simple hierarchy, one pare=
nt</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Multiple inheritance</strong> =E2=86=92 complex, multiple parent=
s, powerful but careful with ambiguity</p></li>
</ul>
