</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ObjectOrientedProgramming(OOP)-1=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3GenericMethods(=
TemplateFunctions)">1=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 <strong>Generic Methods (Template F=
unctions)</strong></h2>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>A method that works with <strong>different types</strong> using a <stron=
g>type parameter</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=E2=9C=85 Example:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
